    "On the industry level, we included the firms' primary industry classification as a control variable.",
    "AI might be more relevant in specific industries, for example, because there are more potential AI use cases in the business context.",
    "We used the first level of the North American Industry Classification System (NAICS).",
    "Each industry is operationalized with a binary control variable.",
    "A list of all included industries is available in Table 2."
